headline: CONMED Corporation Adds Kim Kelderman to its Board of Directors
summary: LARGO, Fla., September 09, 2025--CONMED Corporation (NYSE: CNMD) today announced that Kim Kelderman will be joining its Board of Directors effective September 8, 2025.
